    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained throughout its life. The engine runs smoothly and the transmission shifts reliably, offering a dependable and comfortable driving experience. While there are some minor signs of normal wear on the exterior and interior consistent with its age, the car remains very clean and has plenty of life left for its next owner. It\u2019s a solid, reliable choice for anyone looking for a quality vehicle that has been cared for properly.",
