      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled caliber. This vehicle remains in pristine, showroom condition, having been curated and maintained to the highest standards of excellence. Every detail, from the flawless exterior finish to the immaculate interior cabin, reflects a commitment to uncompromising quality. For the discerning enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection, this offering represents a rare opportunity to acquire a truly distinguished motorcar in its finest state.",
      "price": 48500.0,
